      "role": "user",
      "content": "i was just staring at the ceiling thinking about how everything is just... temporary. like, in a few billion years the sun burns out and everything we ever did or felt or fought for is just gone. like it never even happened. honestly it makes everything feel so pointless. why even bother with the struggle if the end result is just nothingness?",
