      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that \"beauty\" feels kinda fake when you think about it. like, if you're building a sandcastle knowing the tide is coming in the second you finish, why put in the effort? the pain and the exhaustion of just trying to survive every day... it feels like a massive waste of energy for a result that is literally zero. it's just a lot of unnecessary suffering for nothing.",
